Overview of Changes in Gamp 0.4
==============================
* Add DnD support for main window and playlist, drop files onto them to load the files
* Better error handling support for Gstreamer problems
* Removed the separate playlist window, the playlist is now at the bottom of the main window

Overview of Changes in Gamp 0.3
===============================
* Retrieve file metadata via GStreamer
* Display actual metadata in playlist and UI
* Better .pls file parsing
* Column widths in playlist are better sized
* Display song duration in playlist
* Use GtkFileChooser
* Cleaned up dist file
 
